## What board do you have?

You **do NOT have an ESP32** ‚ùå
You have an **ESP8266-based Wi-Fi module** ‚úÖ

Specifically, this line is the giveaway:

> **ESP8266MOD**
> **ISM 2.4GHz**

That means:

* **ESP8266MOD** ‚Üí ESP8266 Wi-Fi module
* **ISM 2.4 GHz** ‚Üí Uses the 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi band
* **‚ÄúWiFi in bolt‚Äù** ‚Üí Just branding / marketing text on the PCB

